Package common

Class WaitingList

java.lang.Object
common.Order
common.WaitingList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class WaitingList extends Order
The WaitingList class represents a waiting list for orders in the system. It extends the Order class and adds attributes specific to the waiting list, such as waiting list ID, place in the list, and waiting list status.

      orderId - The ID of the order associated with the waiting list.
      visitorId - The ID of the visitor making the order.
      parkNumber - The number identifying the park.
      amountOfVisitors - The number of visitors in the order.
      price - The price of the order.

      date - The date of the order.

      telephoneNumber - The telephone number of the visitor.
      parkName - The name of the park associated with the order.
      waitingListId - The ID of the waiting list.
      placeInList - The position of the order in the waiting list.
